<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>هَرِقْ لَنَا مِنْ قَرْقَرى ذَنُوبًا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>إِنَّ الذَّنُوبَ يَنْفَعُ الْمَغْلُوبَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وأَنْشَدَ الكِسَائِيُّ:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«تَنْفَعُ»</span>، مؤنثةً.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وقال بعضُ الشعراءِ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>عَلَى حِينَ مَنْ تَلْبَثْ عَلَيْهِ ذَنُوبُهُ ... يَجِدْ فَقْدَهَا وَفِي الْمَقَامِ تَدَاثُرُ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فأنَّثَها.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وفي سورةِ <span style="color:#947721">{وَالطُّورِ}</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>* <span style="color:#947721">{الْمُسَيْطِرُونَ}</span> بالصادِ والسينِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>* <span style="color:#947721">{وَمَا أَلَتْنَاهُم مِّنْ عَمَلِهِم مِّن شَيْءٍ}</span>،<span style="color:#006d98"> العربُ تقولُ:</span> قد أَلَتَه يَالِتُه،<span style="color:#006d98"> يريدون:</span> نَقَصَه، وهي في غَطَفَانَ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وقال الحُطَيْئَةُ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>أَبْلِغْ بَنِي ثُعَلٍ عَنِّي مُغَلْغَلَةً ... جَهْدَ الرِّسَالَةِ لَا أَلْتًا وَلَا كَذِبَا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>ولغةُ أَسَدٍ وأهلِ <span style="color:#008000">(١)</span> الحجازِ: قد لَاتَه، وهو يَلِيتُه لَيْتًا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span style="color:#006d98">أَنْشَدَنِي بعضُهم:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَمَنْهَلٍ فِيهِ الْغُرَابُ مَيْتُ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَلَيْلَةٍ ذَاتِ دُجًى سَرَيْتُ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) في النسخة: «وَأهْلُ».</p> </div>